## 13. Test Plan Summary

| Area | Test type | Tooling | Key cases covered |
|---|---|---|---|
| DB / RLS | Integration | Vitest + Supabase test project | Cross-org access denial, migration correctness |
| Probe worker | Unit | Vitest + msw/nock | Success, timeout, 5xx, DNS failure, interval respect |
| Evaluation engine | Unit | Vitest, fixture data | Uptime math, p95 math, breach boundary conditions, zero-sample handling |
| Smart contract | Unit | Hardhat + Chai | Access control, payout correctness, double-withdraw prevention |
| API | Integration | Vitest + supertest (or Fastify inject) | Auth, validation, org isolation, pagination |
| Notifications | Unit | Vitest, mocked clients | Template correctness, HMAC verification, retry/backoff |
| Frontend components | Unit | Vitest + React Testing Library | Status rendering, conditional badges |
| Frontend flows | E2E | Playwright | Full signup-to-dashboard flow, responsive breakpoints |

